    <node id="Source1">
      <data key="d0">Source1</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Source1 is a centralized repository containing systematic metadata of biological assays, including taxonomic classifications and detailed experimental attributes.&lt;SEP&gt;Source1 is a data source that provides the Biological_Entries table, detailing biological assay information.</data>
