      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">The Biological_Entries table, found in source1, contains assay details such as unique identifiers, test types, document IDs, curators, taxonomic IDs, strains, source IDs, chemical IDs, subcellular fractions, organisms, cell types, tissues, and descriptions of various biological assays.</data>
