      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Source11 is a data source specifically associated with the study entitled "Proteogenomic Characterization of Endometrial Carcinoma." It serves as the original storage resource and location for the Dou table, also referred to as Dou.csv, from which all related columns and data originate.

Source11 provides detailed clinical, genomic, and proteomic metadata relevant to endometrial cancer patients. The data within Source11 encompasses the semantic context and data column descriptions found in Dou.csv, supporting comprehensive research in endometrial cancer by supplying vital information used in proteogenomic studies.

In summary, Source11 is the definitive repository and contextual reference for the Dou table, offering integral clinical, genomic, and proteomic datasets and associated metadata necessary for advanced biomedical research on endometrial carcinoma.&lt;SEP&gt;Source11 is the reference source or dataset containing the Dou table with clinical, genomic, and proteomic data.&lt;SEP&gt;Source11 is the data source from which the Dou Table and its columns were derived, as specified in the column metadata.&lt;SEP&gt;Source11 is a data source that includes the table Dou and its associated columns.&lt;SEP&gt;Source11 is a data source containing Dou.csv, which includes clinical, genomic, proteomic, and other information for endometrial cancer patients.</data>
