      <data key="d0">Satpathy.csv Table</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">The Satpathy.csv table contains patient data, including sample IDs, participant identifiers, experiment numbers, channel types, tissue types, smoking histories, clinical stages, demographic information, pathology assessments, mutation statuses, molecular and genetic alteration data, immune scores, and purity metrics.&lt;SEP&gt;The Satpathy.csv Table is a dataset containing patient data with columns for sample IDs, participant identifiers, experiment numbers, channel types, tissue types, smoking histories, clinical stages, demographic information, and multiple genomic and clinical characteristics.</data>
